<p><img src="/Content/Images/uploaded/2018_blog/march11.jpg" alt="" width="100" /></p>";}i:19;a:5:{s:4:"guid";s:9:"Blog:4901";s:4:"link";s:68:"http://beatlesradio.com/the-beatles-50-years-ago-today-march-10-1968";s:5:"title";s:46:"The Beatles 50 Years Ago Today: March 10, 1968";s:11:"description";s:57:"<p>The Beatles meditating in India with the Maharishi</p>";s:7:"summary";s:57:"<p>The Beatles meditating in India with the Maharishi</p>";}i:20;a:5:{s:4:"guid";s:9:"Blog:4900";s:4:"link";s:67:"http://beatlesradio.com/the-beatles-50-years-ago-today-march-9-1968";s:5:"title";s:45:"The Beatles 50 Years Ago Today: March 9, 1968";s:11:"description";s:43:"<p>The Beatles are still back in India.</p>";s:7:"summary";s:43:"<p>The Beatles are still back in India.</p>";}i:21;a:5:{s:4:"guid";s:9:"Blog:4899";s:4:"link";s:67:"http://beatlesradio.com/the-beatles-50-years-ago-today-march-8-1968";s:5:"title";s:45:"The Beatles 50 Years Ago Today: March 8, 1968";s:11:"description";s:138:"<p>The Beatles having fun in India</p>
