<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">20. (I Wanna)Testify - The Parliaments</span></p>";}i:244;a:5:{s:4:"guid";s:9:"Blog:4674";s:4:"link";s:67:"http://beatlesradio.com/the-beatles-50-years-ago-today-july-28-1967";s:5:"title";s:45:"The Beatles 50 Years Ago Today: July 28, 1967";s:11:"description";s:781:"<div style="text-align: left;">First : Splashing around on a Greek island</div>
