</div>";}i:274;a:5:{s:4:"guid";s:9:"Blog:4644";s:4:"link";s:67:"http://beatlesradio.com/the-beatles-50-years-ago-today-june-28-1967";s:5:"title";s:45:"The Beatles 50 Years Ago Today: June 28, 1967";s:11:"description";s:481:"<h1 class="title single-title entry-title"><span style="font-size: 10pt;">George Harrison is fined for speeding</span></h1>
