<p><strong><span style="font-size: 10pt;">19. Strawberry Fields Forever - The Beatles</span></strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">20. I'm A Man - Spencer Davis Group</span></p>";s:7:"summary";s:1886:"<h1><span style="font-size: 10pt;">Top 20 Song Chart for April 15, 1967</span></h1>
<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">1. Happy Together - The Turtles</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">2. This is My Song - Petula Clark</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">3. Jimmy Mack - Martha and the Vandellas</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">4. Something Stupid - Frank and Nancy Sinatra</span></p>
