<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;">10. Bernadette - The Four Tops</span></p>";}i:370;a:5:{s:4:"guid";s:9:"Blog:4547";s:4:"link";s:68:"http://beatlesradio.com/the-beatles-50-years-ago-today-march-24-1967";s:5:"title";s:46:"The Beatles 50 Years Ago Today: March 24, 1967";s:11:"description";s:64:"<p>The Beatles in-between recording at EMI Studios in London</p>";s:7:"summary";s:64:"<p>The Beatles in-between recording at EMI Studios in London</p>";}i:371;a:5:{s:4:"guid";s:9:"Blog:4546";s:4:"link";s:68:"http://beatlesradio.com/the-beatles-50-years-ago-today-march-23-1967";s:5:"title";s:46:"The Beatles 50 Years Ago Today: March 23, 1967";s:11:"description";s:635:"<p>Studio Two, EMI Studios in London</p>
